00053 bool
00054 NIVissimSingleTypeParser_Haltestellendefinition::parse(std::istream& from) {
00055     std::string tag;
00056     while (tag != "strecke") {
00057         tag = myRead(from);
00058     }
00059     while (tag != "laenge") {
00060         tag = myRead(from);
00061     }
00062     from >> tag;
00063     tag = readEndSecure(from);
00064     while (tag == "einsteiger" && tag != "DATAEND") {
00065         while (tag != "linie") {
00066             tag = myRead(from);
00067         }
00068         while (tag != "einsteiger" && tag != "DATAEND") {
00069             tag = readEndSecure(from);
00070         }
00071     }
00072     return true;
00073 }
